---
title: Creamy Chorizo & Leek Trottole with Garlic Pangrattato
description: Al dente spirals of trottole pasta combine with a rich creamy sauce and smokey chorizo to create an elegant meal fit for only the
best. Add nutritious greens and a garlic pangrattato for crunch and dinner is complete.

